Executive Profile
Patrick J. Pedonti  Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President, SS&C Technologies Holdings, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 5 different industries.See Board Relationships65$2,431,256As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Patrick J. Pedonti has been the Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of SS&C Technologies Holdings, Inc. since August 2002. Mr. Pedonti has been the Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of SS&C Technologies, Inc. since August 2002. He serves as Senior Vice President and Treasurer of SS&C Fund Administration Services LLC. He serves as Vice President and Treasurer of Financial Models Company Ltd. His responsibilities include financial reporting ... and controls and operational and cost improvements. He served as Vice President and Treasurer at SS&C Technologies, Inc. from May 1999 to August 2002 and served as its Principal Accounting Officer since August 2002. He served as Treasurer at SS&C Technologies Holdings, Inc. from May 1995 to August 2002. Mr. Pedonti served as Vice President and Chief Financial Officer at Accent Color Sciences Inc. from January 1997 to May 1999. He has been a Non-Executive Director of GlobeOp Financial Services S.A since May 31, 2012. He serves as a Director of Financial Models Company Ltd. Mr. Pedonti holds a BS in Accounting from Merrimack College.Read Full Background




