Insider Activity


Individual




Patrick John Louis Pedonti



Mr. Patrick J. Pedonti is Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President at SS&C Technologies Holdings, Inc. and Chief Financial Officer, Treasurer & Senior VP at SS&C Technologies, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at GlobeOp Financial Services SA. Mr. Pedonti was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Vice President by Accent Color Sciences, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Merrimack College.



