Patrick J. Pedonti 
Executive Compensation
As Chief Financial Officer at SS&C TECHNOLOGIES HLDGS INC, Patrick J. Pedonti  made $2,431,256 in total compensation.  Of this total $350,000 was received as a salary, $1,300,000 was received as a bonus, $774,208 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $7,048 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


